    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-spec E46 M3 powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a linear 8,000 RPM power band. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. To address platform-specific longevity, the VANOS solenoid and seals have been overhauled, and the rear subframe mounting points have been reinforced to handle high-torque loads. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative steering and turn-in precision characteristic of the M-chassis. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this an ideal candidate for an enthusiast seeking tactile performance over a static show-piece.",
