      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, showing only the slight, unavoidable stone chips typical of careful highway use. Its body lines remain crisp, and the alloy wheels are free of major curbing. Step inside to find a cabin that has been treated with respect; the premium upholstery is firm and free of tears, while the carpets have been protected by mats since day one. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system and steering wheel controls, functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean, reflecting a history of timely oil changes and preventative maintenance. On the road, the car feels tight and responsive, with smooth gear transitions and confident braking. It is a reliable, high-functioning machine that offers a level of refinement usually reserved for much newer models.",
